# VPS runtime env for the frontend (admin panel) container.
# Copy to /opt/quickboom/frontend.env ON THE VPS and fill in real values.
# Read by docker-compose (env_file) at container start. NEVER goes through GitHub.

# Where Next.js proxies /api/* to (server-side rewrite, resolved at runtime).
# Production backend domain:
BACKEND_API_URL=https://api.voxiqai.com
# Local/in-cluster alternatives:
#   http://backend:5004              (compose service name)
#   http://host.docker.internal:5004 (host-mapped backend)
